com.customlbs.library.model

Class Tiles

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.customlbs.library.model.Tiles
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Tiles
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Model class representing a tile size (zoom level). Each map can have different tile sizes as zoom levels. A detailed description of tile sizes can also be found in the Map description.
